Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是夢是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
