Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自分という心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:09.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:09.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.99,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連這淚水都能將之奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.31,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.31,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:23.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:23.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:23.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要將死亡歎作恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:26.77,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終演を歌う金盞花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:26.77,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鳴唱終演的金盞花
