Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.51,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:37.06,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その根でたくり寄せて
